<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContentb043d04e16cb4afebc1c12e592b53fef">
</div>
<p>The Rheumatology Department aims to improve the health of patients with musculoskeletal (bones, muscles, ligaments and joints) disorders.  The department provides a comprehensive range of services to patients, and uses a multi-disciplinary approach that works closely with the hospital’s orthopaedic, physiotherapy occupational therapy, chronic pain and podiatry departments.</p></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel name-thingsshouldknowmodule">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<h3>Things you should know</h3>
<p>Inpatient (planned) Elective - (Royal Blackburn Hospital and Burnley General Hospital)<br/>Day Case (same day service)- (Royal Blackburn Hospital and Burnley General Hospital)<br/>Outpatients - (Accrington Victoria Hospital, Royal Blackburn Hospital, Burnley General Hospital, Clitheroe Community Hospital, Pendle Community Hospital and Rossendale Hospital)</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
